 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike</strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike spell </strong>deals red lightning dealing also area of<br> effect around impact.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>A secret incantation of the capital's ancient dragon cult.</em><br><em>Summons a red bolt of lightning that scatters and spreads around</em><br><em>the surrounding area.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Charging enhances the range of the lightning bolt.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Spoken of in legend, red lightning is the weapon wielded by the</em><br><em>ancient dragons.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Purchase from <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Brother Corhyn" href="/Brother+Corhyn" target="">Brother Corhyn</a> or&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Miriel Pastor of Vows" href="/Miriel+Pastor+of+Vows">Miriel, Pastor of Vows</a> after giving the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ancient Dragon Prayerbook" href="/Ancient+Dragon+Prayerbook" target="">Ancient Dragon Prayerbook</a>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<img style="width: 18px; height: 18px;" title="item_value_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_value_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px.png" alt="item value icon elden ring wiki guide 18px" width="18" height="18">10,000 Runes.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Ancient Dragons' Lightning Strike Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 31</li> 
 <li>One of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dragon Cult Incantations" href="/Dragon+Cult+Incantations">Dragon Cult Incantations</a> and is boosted by the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Gravel Stone Seal" href="/Gravel+Stone+Seal">Gravel Stone Seal</a></li> 
 <li>Deals lightning damage</li> 
 <li>Does extreme damage to bosses if cast underneath or right next to them, as long as several of the strikes land.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
